cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.NE 

This paper is about image super-resolution using deep neural networks, which is a topic closely related to computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also introduces a new loss function and a dual reconstruction network, which are both related to machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE). Finally, the paper presents experimental results, which involve image processing and analysis (cs.MM). Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-category for this paper is cs.CV, followed by cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, and cs.NE.
